// CSI Ps ' |
//   Request Locator Position (DECRQLP).
//   Valid values for the parameter are:
//     Ps = 0 , 1 or omitted -> transmit a single DECLRP locator
//     report.

//   If Locator Reporting has been enabled by a DECELR, xterm will
